---

<Layout 
  title="Nuestro Equipo"
  description="Conoce a las personas que hacen posible Veredillas FM. Estudiantes apasionados por la comunicación, la tecnología y la creatividad."
  image="/logo.png"
>
    <div class="container page-wrapper">
        <header class="page-header gs-reveal">
            <span class="badge">El Equipo</span>
            <h1>Caras detrás de <br><span class="text-gradient">la Voz</span></h1>
            <p class="subtitle">
                Somos un grupo diverso de estudiantes del IES Veredillas unidos por una misma pasión: conectar con nuestra comunidad a través del audio.
            </p>
        </header>

        <div class="departments gs-reveal">
            {departments.map((dept) => (
                <section class="department-section">
                    <h2 class="dept-title">{dept.title}</h2>
                    <div class="team-grid">
                        {dept.members.map((member) => (
                            <div class="member-card glass-panel">
                                <div class="image-wrapper">
                                    <img src={member.image} alt={member.name} loading="lazy" />
                                </div>
                                <div class="member-info">
                                    <h3>
                                        {member.link ? (
                                            <a href={member.link} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="name-link">
                                                {member.name}
                                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg>
                                            </a>
                                        ) : (
                                            member.name
                                        )}
                                    </h3>
                                    <p class="role">{member.role}</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        ))}
                    </div>
                </section>
            ))}
        </div>

        <!-- Join CTA -->
        <section class="join-cta glass-panel gs-reveal">
            <div class="cta-content">
                <h2>¿Quieres formar parte?</h2>
                <p>Siempre buscamos nuevas voces, guionistas, técnicos y creativos. Si eres alumno del Veredillas, ¡te estamos esperando!</p>
                <a href="/contacto" class="btn btn-primary">Únete al equipo</a>
            </div>
            <div class="cta-decoration">
                <svg width="200" height="200" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mic-icon"><path d="M12 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v7a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3Z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="19" y2="22"/><line x1="8" x2="16" y1="22" y2="22"/></svg>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</Layout>

<script>
    import { gsap } from "gsap";
    
    document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', () => {
        gsap.from(".gs-reveal", {
            y: 30,
            opacity: 0,
            duration: 0.8,
            stagger: 0.2,
            ease: "power2.out"
        });
    });
</script>

<style>
    .page-wrapper {
        padding: 4rem var(--spacing-md);
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .page-header {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto 6rem;
    }

    .badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 50px;
        background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
        color: var(--color-primary);
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
        line-height: 1.1;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 800;
    }

    .subtitle {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Departments */
    .department-section {
        margin-bottom: 5rem;
    }

    .dept-title {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        padding-bottom: 1rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        color: var(--color-text-main);
    }

    .team-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .member-card {
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 20px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .member-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }

    .image-wrapper {
        width: 80px;
        height: 80px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        overflow: hidden;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }

    .image-wrapper img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
    }

    .member-info h3 {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .name-link {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    
    .name-link:hover {
        color: var(--color-primary);
    }

    .role {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
    }

    /* CTA */
    .join-cta {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 4rem;
        border-radius: 30px;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        margin-top: 4rem;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at right bottom, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02));
    }

    .cta-content {
        max-width: 500px;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
    }

    .cta-content h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .cta-content p {
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .cta-decoration {
        position: absolute;
        right: -20px;
        bottom: -40px;
        opacity: 0.05;
        transform: rotate(-15deg);
        pointer-events: none;
    }
    
    .mic-icon {
        width: 300px;
        height: 300px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .join-cta {
            flex-direction: column;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .member-card {
            flex-direction: column;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        
        .image-wrapper {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
    }
</style>
